        <div class="comment clearfix " id="comment-158">
            			                    	<p class="comment-details"><em><a href='http://www.korallenkacke.com/open-thread-old-fogeys-v-young-whippersnappers-ageism-in-tech/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Open Thread: Old Fogeys v. Young Whippersnappers, Ageism in Tech - www.Korallenkacke.com</a></em> | February 24, 2010 at 12:32 am</p>
                    		
            		<div class="comment-text">
