        <div class="comment clearfix " id="comment-211">
            			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7b747d2764678accdcb62440d708df0b?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />                    	<p class="comment-details"><em><a href='http://pakzilla.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Tahir Akram</a></em> | February 27, 2010 at 3:08 pm</p>
                    		
            		<div class="comment-text">
                    		<p>Very interesting topic. &#8220;Age and Programming&#8221;</p>
